title: Episode 250: Double Dicker (Feat. Ebenezer)
itunes:title: Episode 250: Double Dicker (Feat. Ebenezer)
description:
UK R&B artist and producer, Ebenezer, also touches on the time he worked with Beyoncé on an unreleased song for the Lion King soundtrack. Oh, and you'll definitely want to hear how he lost his virginity... Make sure to check out his latest EP, Bad Romantic II. Enjoy!
